scene.message:
Mark: Huh?{wait_fr:32} ...Kido?{nl}
That's you, Kido Reiji!{nl}
What are you doing here?{waitkey}{ret}

{color:2}Kido Reiji.{nl}
A student who transferred{nl}
here half a year ago.{nl}
Quiet. Keeps to himself.{color:0}{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: What on earth was he{nl}
thinking about in a{nl}
place like this...{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Kido's such a gloomy{nl}
dude! Bet he goes home and{nl}
secretly practices magic{nl}
tricks or something!{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: Kido transferred here{nl}
right after the Sebek Building{nl}
went up, didn't he...{waitkey}{nl}
Right, right — we still need{nl}
to get to the hospital.{waitkey}{ret}
